reviewText: .... This is a bunch of stuff from different foreign films and one american - Lethal Seduction..I rented it cause it had Julie Strain in it and she's the queen of 'b'! The film has a lot of humor making fun of the sex scenes and has the cutest hostess, so petite, and sexy. If she works on her delivery she'll be a hot actress for genre films. The way the director and the editor put it all together kept me laughing and enjoying the night!...
